\cf0 \cb2 Albert Rice - UBS Investment Bank, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Ann Hynes - Mizuho Securities USA LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Pito Chickering - Deutsche Bank AG, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Benjamin Mayo - Leerink Partners LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Brian Tanquilut - Jefferies LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Benjamin Hendrix - RBC Capital Markets, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Matthew Gillmor - KeyBanc Capital Markets Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Andrew Mok - Barclays Bank PLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Gabrielle Ingoglia - Cantor Fitzgerald & Co., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Ryan Langston - TD Cowen, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Scott Fidel - Goldman Sachs Group, Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Raj Kumar - Stephens Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Stephen Baxter - Wells Fargo Securities, LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Joshua Raskin - Nephron Research LLC\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Jason Cassorla - Guggenheim Securities, LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Kevin Fischbeck - BofA Securities, Research Division\cb1 \
